### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3001/health

### Register User
POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "demo@streamkita.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "full_name": "Demo User"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "demo@streamkita.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Get Me (replace TOKEN with token from login response)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### Get All Content

GET http://localhost:3001/api/content


### Get Content with Filters

GET http://localhost:3001/api/content?type=MOVIE&page=1&limit=10


### Get Featured Content

GET http://localhost:3001/api/content/featured


### Get Trending Content

GET http://localhost:3001/api/content/trending


### Search Content

GET http://localhost:3001/api/content/search?q=action


### Get Content by ID (replace with actual ID from previous responses)

GET http://localhost:3001/api/content/YOUR_CONTENT_ID


### Set token variable (replace with your token)

@token = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VySWQiOiIxMjU0YTJiOC1mMjFmLTQyYzAtYTFlOC1hOWQwYzBmYjhmNWMiLCJlbWFpbCI6InRlc3RAZXhhbXBsZS5jb20iLCJpYXQiOjE3NjIxNTA1MDEsImV4cCI6MTc2Mjc1NTMwMX0.Qgr37HkIKgbQvKjbwobg3-tc7IJSf-wnK5mul9aH_3k


### Get Profile

GET http://localhost:3001/api/user/profile

Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### Update Profile

PUT http://localhost:3001/api/user/profile

Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

Content-Type: application/json


{
  "full_name": "Updated Name"
}


### Get Watchlist

GET http://localhost:3001/api/user/watchlist

Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### Add to Watchlist (replace CONTENT_ID)

POST http://localhost:3001/api/user/watchlist

Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

Content-Type: application/json


{
  "content_id": "CONTENT_ID_FROM_CONTENT_LIST"
}


### Remove from Watchlist

DELETE http://localhost:3001/api/user/watchlist/CONTENT_ID

Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### Get Watch Progress

GET http://localhost:3001/api/user/watch-progress/CONTENT_ID

Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### Update Watch Progress

PUT http://localhost:3001/api/user/watch-progress/CONTENT_ID

Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

Content-Type: application/json


{
  "progress_seconds": 300
}


### Get Continue Watching

GET http://localhost:3001/api/user/continue-watching

Authorization: Bearer {{token}}